These two files are borrowed from 
  http://opensolaris.org/jive/thread.jspa?messageID=510325
with minor modifications.

After customizing, throw them into 
 /lib/svc/method/postgres_90
 /lib/svc/manifest/application/database/postgresql_90.xml
and import the manifest with
 /usr/sbin/svccfg -v import /lib/svc/manifest/application/database/postgresql_90.xml
